{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e501ac2707","title":"唐歧山在郑州市基层单位党委正副书记会议上的讲话（摘录）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8927339a11","index":0,"year":1976,"month":3,"day":27,"articleId":"e501ac2707"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"877762393f","name":"两条路线斗争","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c","name":"唐岐山同志若干讲话","internal":true,"official":true,"type":"img","author":"唐岐山，复辟后“揭发”材料","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c/1.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c/2.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c/3.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c/4.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c/5.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c/6.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c/7.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c/8.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c/9.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c/10.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c/11.png,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c/12.png"}],"authors":[{"id":"4c54e03b44","name":"唐岐山"}]},"publication_details":{"05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"058328ebcc","type":"paragraph","text":"误，是受邓小平修正主义路线影响。同志们要知道给一个省委定下犯方向路线错误，那可不是一件小事啊r当然对地、市委，对一些单位，问题有大有轻，要通过摆事实讲道；理来定性。同志们讲的，我不排除。","index":0,"publicationId":"05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c","articleId":"e501ac2707"},{"id":"135d8c8f30","type":"paragraph","text":"（根据记录整理）唐岐山三月二十七日在郑州市基层单位党委","index":1,"publicationId":"05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c","articleId":"e501ac2707"},{"id":"5b6b377e90","type":"paragraph","text":"正副书记会议上的讲器（插录）","index":2,"publicationId":"05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c","articleId":"e501ac2707"},{"id":"845b645346","type":"paragraph","text":"“现在有的领导同志由于没有端正对运动的态度，自己不好好学习，也不认真组织群众去学习，我们认为这是错误的。","index":3,"publicationId":"05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c","articleId":"e501ac2707"},{"id":"ef2d9f13dd","type":"paragraph","text":"“要在认真学习的基础上，批判邓小平“三项指示为纲”的修正主义纲领，批判阶级斗争熄灭论”和“唯生产力论”，批判折中主义的说辩论，并且联系我道的实标，彻底揭发批判右倾翻案风。","index":4,"publicationId":"05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c","articleId":"e501ac2707"},{"id":"030752e8eb","type":"paragraph","text":"“受了邓小平错误路线的影响，说了错话，办了错事的，责任在邓小平，希望你们带头揭，带头批，转好弯子。两条路线斗争的阵线已经大白，如果再不转弯子，就是对毛主席的态度问题，持续下去，就会犯新的错误。希望这些同志快转弯，转好弯。只有这样，才能取得反击右倾翻案风的主动权，回到毛主席的革命路线上来。我们认为，在这些同志中，大多数是好的，转的是快的，但是有些人有抵触情结，个别人基至持反对态度。希望有关党的组织帮助他们转变立场，端正态度，积极投入到这场运动中来。","index":5,"publicationId":"05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c","articleId":"e501ac2707"},{"id":"726568c647","type":"paragraph","text":"“当前要管锡有人在那里挑动群众斗群众，以破坏生产来破坏革命，以经济主义转移斗争的大方向。","index":6,"publicationId":"05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c","articleId":"e501ac2707"},{"id":"3983793e16","type":"paragraph","text":"（按当时的记录稿摘录）唐岐山同常建立同志的儿次获话（摘录）第一次。（三月二十三日早上七点半启岐山家里）常，唐师傅，今天静坐三天了。唐。谁叫你们坐的？常。是马志昌。","index":7,"publicationId":"05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c","articleId":"e501ac2707"},{"id":"8288ffb77e","type":"paragraph","text":"常。张永和的问题怎么样？唐：张永和我不知道，过去市委定的小范围霜助，以后为抓了，我就不消楚了。过去糊里翔涂抓了，现在还能里糊涂放，必须得有材料，以后谁也推不翻。铁路上的邢、李。王问题也没有解决麻！","index":8,"publicationId":"05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c","articleId":"e501ac2707"},{"id":"a92754857f","type":"paragraph","text":"常。那现在既然坐下来了，怎么办？唐。回来我给省委说一下，看能不能给个梯子叫您下来。现在坐下来不好起了常。那我们就等吧？唐吹！第二次：（三月二十七日早上，唐岐山家里）常。唐师傅，张永和的问题怎么样了，啥时候能放？公安局已同意送饭了。","index":9,"publicationId":"05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c","articleId":"e501ac2707"},{"id":"0578946e56","type":"paragraph","text":"唐。现在不能放，一放就爆炸了，只能冷放，不能热放，省委已同意调查解决。还有很多工作要作，你们先回去吧！","index":10,"publicationId":"05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c","articleId":"e501ac2707"},{"id":"0b63413513","type":"paragraph","text":"翡德贵。那过去没有调查清楚为啥抓人呢唐：你问我，我问谁？抓，我也不知道么！第豆次：（三月三十日，唐山家）常。张永和能不能放","index":11,"publicationId":"05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c","articleId":"e501ac2707"},{"id":"f09d1c736f","type":"paragraph","text":"唐：你们不是看着的吗？公安局、法院都汇报了情况，记者也跟着的，材料已报上去、等着吧！","index":12,"publicationId":"05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c","articleId":"e501ac2707"},{"id":"637fe99089","type":"paragraph","text":"常。我们厂的问题怎么办","index":13,"publicationId":"05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c","articleId":"e501ac2707"}],"page":{"id":"d26b2a7c4b","publicationId":"05422d8e-4445-44ee-9b50-dcb1f49d143c","articleId":"e501ac2707","start":5,"end":5}}}},"__N_SSG":true}